  "title": "Software Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Us:</strong></p><p>At BYD Singapore, we're driving the future of sustainable transportation with cutting-edge electric vehicles that combine advanced technology, stylish design, and unmatched performance. As a fast-growing company committed to reducing carbon footprints and revolutionizing the automotive industry, we’re looking for a dynamic Software Engineer to join our team and help accelerate our brand’s growth.</p><p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>According to the department planning and the needs of the model project, formulate the product technical scheme; complete the design of the product architecture, software and hardware scheme design and review:</p><p>1. Participate in the analysis of the product software requirements to ensure the feasibility of software requirements</p><p>2. Participate in the design and evaluation of software architecture schemes to ensure that the output complies with the software design and development process requirements for software architecture design specifications</p><p>3. Participate in the implementation of software detailed design, output code or model in accordance with coding standards</p><p>4. Participate in the implementation unit verification, output static check report, code review report</p><p>5. Participate in the implementation of software component integration strategies to ensure efficient coordination between different modules</p>",
